<h2 id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-=F0=9F=A4=94Assumptions">=F0=9F=
=A4=94 Assumptions</h2>
<h3 id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-UserAssumptions">User Assumption=
s</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Primary household managers (71% mothers) spend 2-3 hours daily on coordi=
nation tasks</p></li>
<li>
<p>83% of primary managers feel overwhelmed by mental load</p></li>
<li>
<p>Families currently use 10-15 different apps for household management</p>=
</li>
<li>
<p>91% express frustration with app fragmentation</p></li>
<li>
<p>Users willing to pay $9.99/month for comprehensive solution that reduces=
 cognitive burden</p></li>
<li>
<p>Target market: 50M+ dual-income families with children aged 5-18 in US</=
p></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-TechnicalAssumptions">Technical =
Assumptions</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>React Native New Architecture (v0.76+) is production-ready and stable</p=
></li>
<li>
<p>Bun runtime provides 3x faster performance than Node.js for backend oper=
ations</p></li>
<li>
<p>PostgreSQL Row-Level Security effectively isolates multi-tenant data</p>=
</li>
<li>
<p>On-device voice processing (Expo Speech Recognition) provides adequate a=
ccuracy for family use</p></li>
<li>
<p>Google Cloud Platform provides reliable AI infrastructure with 99.9% upt=
ime</p></li>
<li>
<p>Gemini 2.0 Flash model sufficient for 85% of AI operations; Gemini 3.0 P=
ro for complex reasoning</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>MCP (Model Context Protocol)</strong> can be implemented within =
10-week timeline</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>A2UI (Agent-to-UI)</strong> can be delivered in phased approach =
within MVP</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-BusinessAssumptions">Business As=
sumptions</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Google Cloud Startup Credits ($200K) will be secured to offset initial i=
nfrastructure costs</p></li>
<li>
<p>Self-hosted architecture achieves 90% cost savings vs. managed service a=
lternatives</p></li>
<li>
<p>Operating costs at scale: $0.68 per family per month (infrastructure $15=
7 + AI $190 for 500 families)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Product Hunt launch generates 1,000+ early adopters and validates produc=
t-market fit</p></li>
<li>
<p>Beta testing with 20-30 families provides sufficient feedback for refine=
ment</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-DevelopmentAssumptions">Developm=
ent Assumptions</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>3-person team (mobile, backend, web/admin) can deliver MVP in 10 weeks</=
p></li>
<li>
<p>6-epic structure covers all critical MVP functionality including MCP and=
 A2UI</p></li>
<li>
<p>Phased AI rollout (basic text =E2=86=92 MCP integration =E2=86=92 A2UI c=
ontrol) manages technical complexity</p></li>
<li>
<p>Zero-downtime deployments achievable with proper architecture and CI/CD<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<h2 id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-=E2=AD=90Milestones">=E2=AD=90 M=
ilestones</h2>
<h3 id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-10-WeekDevelopmentRoadmap">10-We=
ek Development Roadmap</h3>
<p><strong>Epic 1: Authentication &amp; Family Management</strong> (Week 1-=
2)</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Self-hosted authentication system using Better Auth</p></li>
<li>
<p>Family workspace creation and member management</p></li>
<li>
<p>Invitation system with email/SMS notifications</p></li>
<li>
<p>Role-based access control (admin, member, child)</p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Epic 2: Core Data Modules</strong> (Week 3-5)</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Calendar &amp; Scheduling with AI-powered conflict detection</p></li>
<li>
<p>Tasks &amp; Chores with intelligent assignment logic</p></li>
<li>
<p>Shared Lists with categories and smart suggestions</p></li>
<li>
<p>Expense Tracking with split calculations and budget tracking</p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Epic 3: Communication &amp; Documents</strong> (Week 6)</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Family Feed with chronological activity timeline</p></li>
<li>
<p>Document Vault with AES-256 encryption</p></li>
<li>
<p>OCR for receipts and document scanning (Google Vision API)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Photo and document sharing with comments</p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Epic 4: Meal Planning</strong> (Week 7)</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Recipe database and weekly meal planner</p></li>
<li>
<p>Automatic grocery list generation from meal plans</p></li>
<li>
<p>Dietary restriction and allergy support</p></li>
<li>
<p>Meal rotation suggestions and nutrition tracking</p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Epic 5: AI Integration with MCP &amp; A2UI</strong> (Week 8)</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Model Context Protocol (MCP) Implementation</strong>: 52 standar=
dized tools across 7 modules</p></li>
<li>
<p>Basic AI text responses via chat interface</p></li>
<li>
<p>Voice input/output with on-device processing</p></li>
<li>
<p>Orchestrator AI + 7 specialist agents (Task, Calendar, Finance, List, Fe=
ed, Document, Meal)</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Agent-to-UI (A2UI) Foundation</strong>: AI navigation and compon=
ent control system</p></li>
<li>
<p>90% context caching for cost optimization</p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Epic 6: Real-time Sync &amp; Polish</strong> (Week 9-10)</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>WebSocket implementation for real-time synchronization</p></li>
<li>
<p>Push notifications for critical events</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>A2UI Enhancement</strong>: Screen navigation, component highligh=
ting, action execution</p></li>
<li>
<p>UI/UX polish and accessibility improvements</p></li>
<li>
<p>Performance optimization and bug fixes</p></li>
<li>
<p>Beta testing with 20-30 early adopter families</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-=F0=9F=93=9DRequirements">=F0=9F=
=93=9D Requirements</h2>
<h3 id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-CoreFunctionalRequirements">Core=
 Functional Requirements</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p><strong>Requirement</strong></p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p><strong>User Story</strong></p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p><strong>Importance</strong></p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p><strong>Jira Issue</strong></p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p><strong>Notes</strong></p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Self-hosted Authentication</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>As a family, I want to create an account without relying on third-party =
auth providers for privacy</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>HIGH</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Better Auth implementation</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Family Member Invitations</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>As a family admin, I want to invite members via email/SMS so they can jo=
in our workspace</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>HIGH</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Supports email and SMS delivery</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Shared Calendar with AI Conflict Detection</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>As Sarah, I want the AI to automatically detect scheduling conflicts acr=
oss all family members</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>HIGH</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Cross-member conflict analysis</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>AI-Powered Task Assignment</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>As a parent, I want tasks automatically assigned fairly based on availab=
ility, skills, and workload</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>HIGH</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Fairness algorithm required</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Voice-First Interface</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>As Mike, I want to interact with the app using voice commands while driv=
ing or multitasking</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>HIGH</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>On-device processing only</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Multi-Agent AI System with MCP</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>As a user, I want specialized AI agents using standardized tools for con=
sistent behavior</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>HIGH</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>8 agents + 52 MCP tools</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Agent-to-UI (A2UI) Control</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>As a user, I want AI to navigate screens and execute actions for me inst=
ead of just telling me what to do</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>HIGH</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Screen navigation, component manipulation</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Real-time Synchronization</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>As a family member, I want changes to sync instantly across all family m=
embers' devices</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>HIGH</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>WebSocket implementation</p></td>
